    57	  slow clock, tiny trigger, strong amplifier, rotor-mediated exchange, and
    58	  one-way next-shell transfer. Exploration 002 treats exact-NS coefficient
    59	  rigidity precisely as the threat to reproducing this hierarchy. The role
    60	  hierarchy is therefore part of the object, not merely a later theorem lens.
