    87	
    88	The most likely presentable output is not a single canonical theorem object. It is either:
    89	
    90	- a tighter bounded negative result saying every plausible notion fails for a named reason after exact interaction analysis, or
    91	- a split outcome in which one leakage-style notion and one behavior-style notion survive as distinct downstream targets.
    92	
